### 💼 Projects

### 📂 Get All Projects
GET {{baseUrl}}/Projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 📂 Get My Projects (by User ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/Projects?userId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ➕ Create New Project
POST {{baseUrl}}/Projects
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Gotham Surveillance System",
  "description": "Real-time crime prediction using ML + Computer Vision",
  "projectUrl": "https://batnet.tech",
  "githubUrl": "https://github.com/brucewayne/gotham-surveillance",
  "technologies": ["C#", ".NET", "OpenCV", "Azure"],
  "imageUrls": ["https://example.com/batproject1.jpg"]
}

### 🛠️ Update Project
PUT {{baseUrl}}/Projects/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Updated Gotham Surveillance System",
  "description": "Improved real-time system with enhanced facial detection",
  "projectUrl": "https://batnet.tech/v2",
  "githubUrl": "https://github.com/brucewayne/gotham-surveillance-v2",
  "technologies": ["C#", ".NET 8", "OpenCV", "Redis", "Azure"],
  "imageUrls": ["https://example.com/batupdate.jpg"]
}

### ❌ Delete Project
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/Projects/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

